snippet.title: Lucky Hero | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
▸Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2404510/

Lucky Hero is a roguelike symbol-building game. Engage in battles with a variety of enemies by spinning the wheel of fortune, collecting, and combining various symbols and skills!

The game will be released on Steam, NOV 16.

Twitter: Neverland Entertainment
YouTube: Neverland_Entmt
